data.description: WOW! If you are looking for an amazing home with lots of updates, you may want to take the time to stop at this lovely cape cod! Well kept exterior is inviting with a gorgeous front porch! The interior is so neat and tidy. Check out the Remodeled kitchen, and the dinette space is open and inviting. Beautiful new white cabinets and awesome butcher block counter tops, kitchen appliances are negotiable. The room is completed with a rustic wood accent wall in the spacious dinette. The living room has beautiful updated laminate wood flooring, modern paint tones, a wood burning fireplace plus a coat closet. All the doors have been changed to white 6 panel doors and fixtures are modern as well. Two large carpeted first floor bedrooms and a full bath complete the first floor. Upstairs is an enormous second floor bedroom, neutrally carpeted and painted with closet and built in dresser and storage cabinet. The full basement is semi finished and is used as a huge family room! Large half bath with space to expand and make a full! Large utility room, huge laundry room. Owners state the basement was Previously waterproofed by old owners as well. Glass block windows, updated furnace Spring 2022. There is central air as well! Vinyl windows. Sump pump Updated in 2022, the new concrete drive stretches back to the detached two car garage, concrete patio, fire pit area and raised garden! Partially fenced. This is a home you will be so happy you came to see! Call today!
